pageContext.claim: “Well first of all, you know, remember the famous question when she [Hillary Clinton] asked me whether or not I would accept the results of the election? You know, she felt pretty confident until the end of that debate and frankly she was very strong. Do -- would you accept the results of the election? Well, she didn't accept the results. She still hasn't.”
pageContext.analysis: Hillary Clinton called Trump to concede on Election Day 2016 and publicly said she wished him success.
